  <brief_title>Effects of tDCS on Quadriceps Strength After Stroke</brief_title>
  <acronym>tDCS(HE)</acronym>
  <official_title>a Controlled, Randomized Study Evaluating the Immediate Effect of One tDCS Session on Quadriceps Strength in Hemiparetic Patients.</official_title>
